premise_source_doc_sentence: Earth-Two Wonder Woman had appeared several months earlier in one comic-book panel .

He first appeared in the summer of 1942 in Wonder Woman # 1 , volume 1 , written by Wonder Woman creator William Moulton Marston , and went on to become one of Wonder Woman 's principal Golden Age foes .
The Earth-Two Wonder Woman was first featured as a character separate from Wonder Woman  (  known as Earth-One Wonder Woman  )  in the second Jay Garrick and Barry Allen comic .
The Wonder Woman Chronicles : Volume 1 collects material from All Star Comics # 8 , Sensation Comics # 1 -- 9 , and Wonder Woman # 1 ; March 23 , 2010 ; ISBN 978-1-4012-2644-2
The Wonder Woman Chronicles : Volume 3 collects material from Wonder Woman # 4 -- 5 , Sensation Comics # 15 -- 18 , and Comic Cavalcade # 2 ; December 4 , 2012 ; ISBN 978-1-4012-3692-2
